detected but that was another matter. After the decapataiona large ship had

pieces of Megastrom and rebuilt him. They didnt tell him who they where and

and awaied the return of his brother. He didnt know how he knew it was 
comeing but iut was. When he detected him he immediatly went off towrds 
earth. He then landed here..
